Package: qctimeseries
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Quality Control for Time-Series Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anthony", "Darrouzet-Nardi",
           email = "adarrouzetnardi@gmail.com",
           role  = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A Shiny-based visual tool that uses interactive brushing to
    inspect and flag bad data points in numeric time-series datasets up to
    a few million rows.  Features include arbitrary POSIXct time columns,
    window-by-window navigation, per-point or bulk flagging, and an optional
    secondary-variable overlay panel.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
